    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 across all five COU operating points with a mean absolute error of 0.043. The assessment team acknowledges that validation runs were executed under solver build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7; the patch difference is limited to an I/O logging routine and is considered immaterial to numerical results. The credibility package is accepted in support of the 510(k) submission for the Class II CPB device.",
